{"tid":1357490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家既差佬退休係食長糧定公積金?","createTime":"2019-07-23T17:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:07:58.000Z","uid":1260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4944b50e26425a54fd29204320f36317d0fb42f5","tid":1357490,"uid":1260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"久唔久就見到有D什麼警察老婆話老公頂唔順想辭職<br />\n早兩日咩謝曬皮IG又話有差佬貼埋委任證想洗底唔撈<br />\n仲要俾其他差佬起到底<br />\n其實如果政府內部調職/辭職唔影響長糧/公職金既<br />\n呢班所謂睇唔過眼想做番人既差佬<br />\n不如你地唔好&quot;辭職&quot;啦<br />\n下次出動去最前線...同示威者對立既時候除頭盔企過黎<br />\n橫掂你地貼委任證俾人起到底既都會屈你藏有CP<br />\n除頭盔過黎最多話你失職炒架咋<br />\n但係電視影住同你暗啞底辭職差好遠架<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6FyLeHl_K3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6FyLeHl_K3A&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=5d526e0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6FyLeHl_K3A</a>"},{"pid":"11bde7397c1359e27421f7f684a383922aae6e03","tid":1357490,"uid":1260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3a20a21072ea3bb4e34778d613528f7f2550ce","tid":1357490,"uid":1260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"今日有委任證添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}